1.) Create an HTML, CSS and JavaScript File
2.) Create main.js with the following code:
  (function() {
    'use strict'
      // your code will start here...
      
      console.log('main.js loaded');
      
      // and end here
}())
3.)Create the CSS file, main.css with the following code:

  /* Styles go here */
  
4.)Create the HTML file called index.html with the following code:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="main.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>My first application</h1>
    <p>Welcome to <i>Learning JavaScript</i></p>
    
    <script src="main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
